---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Stacks Bitcoin Unleashed 2024 — AES" bodyClass="inner-page">

  <div class="container-fluid event-hero">
    <div class="event-hero-inner">
      <div class="event-hero-left">
        <div class="event-location">Singapore</div>
        <div class="event-title">Stacks<br />Bitcoin<br />Unleashed<br />2024</div>
        <div class="event-tagline">
          A half-day meet-up mashed up with community announcements alongside Token2049 at the Fullerton Hotel for 300 attendees.
        </div>
        <div class="event-hero-photo">
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work1.png')"></div>
          <div class="event-hero-photo-item" style="background-image: url('/images/work2.png')"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-hero-right">
        <div class="event-detail-card">
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Format</div>
            <p>Positioned alongside Token2049 — one of the most attended crypto weeks in Asia — this half-day format was designed to punch above its weight. The Fullerton Hotel provided a premium setting that matched the caliber of the broader conference week surrounding it.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">Programming</div>
            <p>The event blended community meetup energy with formal on-stage announcements, giving Stacks a focused moment to speak directly to 300 engaged attendees. The hybrid format kept energy high while delivering meaningful content for both developers and ecosystem stakeholders.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="event-detail-block">
            <div class="event-detail-heading">On-Site</div>
            <p>Singapore's Token2049 week brings a global audience to the city, and co-locating gave Stacks access to that concentrated network. A tight execution at a world-class venue made the most of a condensed timeline and delivered an experience that felt intentional at every touchpoint.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-gallery">
    <div class="event-gallery-inner">
      <div class="gallery-grid">
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work3.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work5.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder" style="background-image: url('/images/work7.png')"></div>
        <div class="gallery-placeholder gallery-large" style="background-image: url('/images/work9.png')"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid event-back">
    <div class="event-back-inner">
      <a href="/work" class="cr-btn white ex-padding">← Back to All Events</a>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
